        "parent": "",
        "content": "\u003c@!301186049323958275\u003e question re: the 7 wei minimum",
        "created_at": "2021-07-05T17:50:53.583000+00:00",
        "attachments": null
    },
    {
        "author": "timbeiko",
        "category": "Channel Graveyard",
        "parent": "",
        "content": "what is the \"math quirk\" that makes that the effective minimum?",
        "created_at": "2021-07-05T17:51:01.297000+00:00",
        "attachments": null
    },
    {
        "author": "timbeiko",
        "category": "Channel Graveyard",
        "parent": "",
        "content": "8 is the first number which multiplied by 1.125 gives a greater integer",
        "created_at": "2021-07-05T17:51:22.505000+00:00",
        "attachments": null
    },
    {
        "author": "timbeiko",
        "category": "Channel Graveyard",
        "parent": "",
        "content": "and if we round up starting at .5, then 5*1.125 would work too because it's 5.625",
        "created_at": "2021-07-05T17:51:43.783000+00:00",
        "attachments": null
    },
    {
        "author": "sky.cactus",
        "category": "Channel Graveyard",
        "parent": "",
        "content": "`7/8 == 0`, so if the parent base fee is 7 and the block is empty, we'll get a base fee delta of 7/8 which means we get a delta of 0.",
        "created_at": "2021-07-05T17:54:45.141000+00:00",
        "attachments": null
    },
    {
        "author": "timbeiko",
        "category": "Channel Graveyard",
        "parent": "",
        "content": "So we calculate the _delta_ and not the \"newBaseFee\", right?",
        "created_at": "2021-07-05T17:55:53.468000+00:00",
        "attachments": null
    },
    {
        "author": "sky.cactus",
        "category": "Channel Graveyard",
        "parent": "",
        "content": "And `8 - 1/8 == 7`, so we can walk down to 7 but not further.",
        "created_at": "2021-07-05T17:56:11.372000+00:00",
        "attachments": null
    },
    {
        "author": "sky.cactus",
        "category": "Channel Graveyard",
        "parent": "",
        "content": "We calculate the delta and then subtract that from the parent base fee.",
        "created_at": "2021-07-05T17:56:31.911000+00:00",
        "attachments": null
    },
    {
        "author": "sky.cactus",
        "category": "Channel Graveyard",
        "parent": "",
        "content": "```\nnewBaseFee = parentBaseFee - parentBaseFee * (parentGasTarget - parentGasUsed) // parentGasTarget // 8\n```",
        "created_at": "2021-07-05T17:58:12.967000+00:00",
        "attachments": null
    },
    {
        "author": "sky.cactus",
        "category": "Channel Graveyard",
        "parent": "",
        "content": "Where `//` rounds down for positive values.",
        "created_at": "2021-07-05T17:58:29.353000+00:00",
        "attachments": null
    },
    {
        "author": "timbeiko",
        "category": "Channel Graveyard",
        "parent": "",
        "content": "Got it.",
        "created_at": "2021-07-05T17:59:04.452000+00:00",
        "attachments": null
    },
    {
        "author": "timbeiko",
        "category": "Channel Graveyard",
        "parent": "",
        "content": "Thanks ðŸ™‚",
        "created_at": "2021-07-05T17:59:08.408000+00:00",
        "attachments": null
    },
    {
